summary: I've started editing my next YouTube video! It is about BACTERIA. More specifically, it is the first video in a series on...
caption: I’ve started editing my next YouTube video! It is about BACTERIA. More specifically, it is the first video in a series on pathogens – next I’ll cover viruses & viroids, then all other things that can make people sick (funguses, parasites, etc). And then I’m going to be talking about specific plagues & diseases. So far I know I’m going to talk about the bubonic plague & lyme disease. If you have a favorite plague/disease, let me know so I can put it on my list! How is everyone else’s Saturday going? <3
